{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbdc4df19-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6901a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6901a"},"text":"§ 6901a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Congressional findings: used oil recycling","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Congress finds and declares that—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbdc4df1a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6901a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" used oil is a valuable source of increasingly scarce energy and materials;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbdc4df1b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6901a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" technology exists to re-refine, reprocess, reclaim, and otherwise recycle used oil;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbdc4df1c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s6901a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" used oil constitutes a threat to public health and the environment when reused or disposed of improperly; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"that, therefore, it is in the national interest to recycle used oil in a manner which does not constitute a threat to public health and the environment and which conserves energy and materials.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbdc4df1d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/463/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–463, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-15"},"text":"Oct. 15, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2055"},"text":"94 Stat. 2055","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbdc4df1e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbdc4df1f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbdc4df20-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Used Oil Re­cycling Act of 1980, and not as part of the Solid Waste Disposal Act which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
